dc_description_s: This data layer represents public lands for Dane County, Wisconsin at year-end 2017. It is a feature classes within the geodatabase, Dane_PublicLands_2017.gdb.
uw_supplemental_s: For the most recent version of this dataset please visit: https://lio.countyofdane.com/ This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2018. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2017. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2018.
